%h1 Lost Tweets

%div.tweet
  %p.info
    = link_to("@zeke", "http://twitter.com/zeke")
    accidentally deleted his twitter account, but had a 
    chance to save his tweets before they vanished into the ether.

- @tweets.each do |tweet|
  %div.tweet
    %p= tweetify_text(tweet.text)
    %p.date= time_ago_in_words_or_date tweet.tweeted_at
    
%div.footer
  %p
    A
    = link_to("Zeke Sikelianos", "http://zeke.sikelianos.com")
    project. Source code at 
    = link_to("github.com/zeke/losttweets", "http://github.com/zeke/losttweets") + "."